Package com.mku.salmonfs.handler

Class AesStreamHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.net.URLStreamHandler
      • com.mku.salmonfs.handler.AesStreamHandler
  • public class AesStreamHandler
extends java.net.URLStreamHandler
    Provides a local stream URL handler to read an AesFile as a source. This works with 3rd party libraries and apps that can read file only via URLs.
